title: DINAIR AIRBRUSH MAKEUP - VANILLA- 1.15 OZ. FAIR SKIN COMPLEXION
description: Dinair is THE leader in airbrush foundation makeup coverage for flawless daily wear, High Definition makeup for picture perfect photos and videos. Dinair is the originator of the airbrush makeup which revolutionized the cosmetics industry. For over 30 years Dinair has been the choice for salons and professional makeup artists worldwide and is the leading innovator of airbrush makeup, systems and accessories. Dinair has also provided professional airbrush makeup training since the 1980's to leading makeup artists all around the world. Unlike traditional makeup (where you rub makeup into your skin), airbrushing sprays a fine mist, so the makeup "sits evenly" on your skin. Airbrush makeup provides flawless coverage (sheer or opaque), by minimizing skin imperfections while giving skin a beautifully natural looking finished result.
